name: Robot Metropolis Carnival Series 9/10
description: The Robot Metropolis Carnival. Another addition to the entertainment had to be made. Nobody knows how exactly it works, but those who see it in person are struck with awe and spend all their money on it. A true masterpiece. Now, who shall receive credit? The creator? The creator of the creator? The creator of the creator of the creator? Philosophers will bend their minds for aeons to come as they attempt to answer that question. Visitors of the carnival will do no such thing and focus on the object itself.
